Some Updates on Abundance ($0.027/$0.028)Abundance wholly owned subsidiary OSC (Orient Salt chemical) took shares in Chinese listed co. Jiangsu Sopo (JS)They paid RMB 30mil for 3 610 108 new shares of JS at RMB 8.31 giving them 0.31% of the enlarged capital of JS back in Mar21.As of Friday  JS is trading at RMB 17.20.This means that initial investment of RMB 30mil has doubled and earned them a handsome paper gain of approx. RMB 32mil which equates to $6.67 million sgd as of 19th June 2021.DYODD
